prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant and humorous anime romantic comedy scene, greeting card front cover, flat 2D vector art style.

The setting is a beautiful park under a large, blooming cherry blossom tree. Pink petals are gently falling and swirling through the air, creating a dreamy, ethereal atmosphere.

The female character, with a comically surprised and flustered expression, is mid-stumble, tripping forward dramatically with one leg kicked up behind her. She is reaching her arms out in front of her. She wears the light grey hoodie with the hood up, and dark pants as seen in the photos.

The male character is lunging forward to catch her in a classic, over-the-top anime hero pose. He has one arm outstretched to catch her and a charming, slightly goofy, confident grin on his face. He is wearing the black zip-up hoodie and dark pants.

The entire scene is filled with dramatic shoujo anime effects: sparkling light motes, soft focus blurs around the edges, and dynamic speed lines radiating from the couple to emphasize the action and humor. The color palette is bright and cheerful with pastel pinks, soft blues, and lush greens, evoking a dreamy fantasy feel.

In the center of the card, in a beautiful, flowing, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday to my favorite leading lady!"
